Sentencas: Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) is a promising cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However, BSCF cathode performance stability has been a challenge and its electrochemical performance deteriorates severely in the presence of Cr2O3-forming metallic interconnect.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: We demonstrate that LaCoO3-delta (LC) coating on BSCF cathode can not only enhance BSCF electrochemical performance, but also effectively improve the BSCF performance stability.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this study, LC-coated BSCF-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.9 (LC@BSCF-GDC) cathode is prepared through a solution impregnation method and systematically characterized.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: EIS, XRD, Raman, SEM and EDS tests with and without SUS430 interconnect are conducted to characterize the Cr-tolerance.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results show that BSCF-GDC cathode is susceptible to Cr poisoning while LC@BSCF-GDC cathode has significantly enhanced tolerance to Cr poisoning.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Single cells with LC@BSCF-GDC cathode achieve higher peak power density and smaller polarization resistance values than single cells with BSCF-GDC cathode.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, significant improvement of performance stability under a constant current load has been achieved for single cells with LC@BSCF-GDC cathode.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This work provides a new solution for solving BSCF cathode performance stability.
Titulo: LaCoO3-δ coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
